O '''Gîv''' (vay ''Gîyu'', ''Gêsu'', ''Dîv'') si yek [[char]] so si o may importanto xaben manushengo.

==Anav==
O lav si [[Indo-ariaynikane ćhiba|indo-ariyanikanes]] ([[sanskritikanes]]: गोधूमा - Godhuma; [[hindi ćhib|Hindikanes]]: गेहूं - Gehun).

==Puranipen==
Anglunes, le manusha baryarden o giv andi [[Sudvestutni Asiya]], 10,000 [[bersh]]a anglal. 5.000 bersha anglal, lesko baryaripen avilo ande [[Ethiopia|Etopiya]], [[Indiya]], [[Republika Irland|Galyero]] tay [[Spaniya]]. Palal 1,000 bersha avilo vi andi [[China|Shîn]]

